name: 樹里
text:
あとちょっとで、決勝のステ－ジか
アタシ、本当にここまで来たんだな
trans:
Just a little longer and it'll be the final competition.
I really made it all the way here.

name: 樹里
text:
いや、逆にワクワクしてる気がする
早くステ－ジに出て、踊りたいっつ－か……
trans:
Nah, I actually think I'm excited.
It's like, I can't wait to get on stage and dance...

name: 樹里
text:
さっきまで緊張が残ってたけど、今は全然ね－んだ
ヘンだと思うか？
trans:
I was still a bit nervous until just a little while ago but now I don't feel it at all.
Isn't that weird?

name: プロデューサー
text:
変じゃないさ
むしろ、度胸があっていいと思うぞ
trans:
It's not weird.
Actually, I think it's great that you've found your courage.

name: 樹里
text:
そっか。まあ、こういう大舞台に出るのは目標だったから、
嬉しさの方が勝ってるのかもな
trans:
Ah, good. I mean, it was my goal to appear in major events like this so
I guess I'm happy more than anything.

name: プロデューサー
text:
気持ちはわかるが、喜ぶのはまだ早いぞ、樹里
泣いても笑っても、これで全部決まるんだ
trans:
I know how you feel but it's too early to celebrate
now, Juri. No matter what happens, this is where
everything will be settled once and for all.

name: プロデューサー
text:
全力でやって、悔いが残らないような
最高のステ－ジを見せてくれ！
trans:
Go all out, leave behind no regrets,
and show us all your greatest performance!

name: 樹里
text:
よし、わかった
行ってくるから、最後まで見てろよな！
trans:
Right, got it.
I'm off so don't stop watching 'til it's over!
